thread.title: T-Boz

author: T-Boz
title: T-Boz
text: The ease and accuracy of the request form quickly paired us with several potential candidates. Breanna submitted a reasonable bid and her GigSalad profile included a photo, brief bio, and video clip of her singing. We booked her effortlessly on line and were immediately linked directly to her. Breanna was punctual, professional and a perfect singer who warmly consoled the bereaved through song. We couldn't be more pleased.
